short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Allows you to make calls through your Soho66 account from your context menu

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
For all Soho66 customers, this extension will allow you to place calls from your web browser, making use of the "Dial By URL" feature that is enabled on all accounts.

Simply set up your extensions through the Options menu, and then highlight and right-click on a telephone number in a web page, and select which extension you want to dial out from!

**********
Whilst built to interact with the Soho66 "Dial By URL" functionality, this extension is not officially affiliated with Soho66 in any way.
**********
